<L>__{interior apartment later}
<A>__{they eat.}
<C>__{julie}
<D>__{so what were you in prison for, max?}
<A>__{max slurps his coffee.}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{i'm a confidence man.}
<C>__{julie}
<D>__{you mean a `con' man?}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{i never liked that word. it's only half of what it is. the word confidence comes from the latin. fides. with faith. belief.}
<P>__{(then)}
<D>__{that's what i'm about.}
<A>__{she considers this.}
<C>__{julie}
<D>__{you mean you make people feel good...and then you rip them off?}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{yes.}
<A>__{he glances at henry.}
<C>__{max }
<D>__{but i was always much better at the feeling good part than the ripping off part.}
<P>__{(then)}
<D>__{hence, the prison.}
<C>__{julie}
<D>__{aren't you guys worried about getting caught?}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{not really. for me it's a win win situation.}
<C>__{julie}
<D>__{how?}
<C>__{max}
<D>__{i like jail. three hots and a cot.}
