<D>__{so why would you take the risk? is it the money?}
<A>__{henry doesn't answer, starts to collect the plates.}
<C>__{julie }
<D>__{it must be the money.}
<A>__{henry smiles.}
<C>__{julie }
<D>__{you are a criminal. a greedy little criminal.}
